n守衛香港 保護香港人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以武制暴</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>香港防衛隊由保安公司做起<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344373\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344373</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n琴晚兩大焦點<br />\n<br />\n1. 上環無預警地開槍企圖殺害市民，令人群，記者恐慌及受傷！<br />\n<br />\n2. 國家恐怖組織喺元朗入侵西鐵站暴打市民，警方以無武器或合法集結放過恐怖組織。"},{"pid":"8647eff8f33c292cad097f1d477cade728fde2af","tid":1346841,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9e3322e82b7e6643ea9aed173f5b91248dd15091","tid":1346841,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd1802be5a74aa11d457d3daefe83ebe77949330","tid":1346841,"uid":123688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"97d517091a3c34762495926e5a0d883569b8c04c","tid":1346841,"uid":205774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"505ff1d52a469f053050d4208c88f0d1b47b3318","tid":1346841,"uid":279874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b039570f5e8e0248cdacb87482c569fff0ef2ce7","tid":1346841,"uid":15943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:07:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf901f394edab9535bab7ec740b4bff2982e4c22","tid":1346841,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"043ca9649b80f31a7a49fc056db8c422a1c2958b","tid":1346841,"uid":281418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:08:58.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"61e140d3cf29c8620d16a31d4ca872f17a09519e","tid":1346841,"uid":28728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":