警合作，如果唔係件事會變左人民鬥人民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721 警黑之夜 - 整合 (上環 + 元朗)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！<br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"94af6d5cb5675298d83c063e3b80b83bcc76b702","tid":1346841,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"030971003f35da3fc488be6fe3bc28d6b43b0b50","tid":1346841,"uid":108203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db25c44aac4bcab913358568839553b2082af5d","tid":1346841,"uid":108203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ac94494f71a7e9fcb81c6ab02e91a99bac53777","tid":1346841,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:10:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a77b3b152caf88c3b721b1e55d86c847a4036d79","tid":1346841,"uid":258003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:12:25.000Z","msg":"打住本民前 光復香港，時代革命 的旗幟，去處置香港之蛆蟲-黑幫"},{"pid":"ebbb4d03beac67336170c2ce9a0e2a1194488108","tid":1346841,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"